Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.02,0:23:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.56,0:23:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你出道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.91,0:23:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
